Description_lang: Whenever nearby allies take damage, the Voice has a chance to beckon you. Upon hearing its call $409442u times you fully submit to its influence, stealing $s2 of the $s4 nearest allies' lowest secondary stat, and giving you the stolen amount plus $s1 to your highest secondary stat for $409447d.
AuraDescription_lang: The star whispers to $@auracaster. Taking damage has a chance to grant them a stack of The Voice Beckons. Once at $409442u, they will reduce the lowest secondary stat of their $w4 nearest allies by $w2 while granting themselves up to ${$w1+$w3*4} of their highest secondary for $409447d.
